
sequenceDiagram
    participant TX as pkt_enhanced_tx.py
    participant Codec as packet_codec.py
    participant FEC as fec_cc.py
    participant Mod as BPSK Modulator
    participant Radio as SoapySDR/HackRF
    participant Air as RF Channel
    participant RX as pkt_enhanced_rx.py
    
    TX->>Codec: packet_encode(payload_bytes)
    Codec->>Codec: prepend length(2B), append CRC-32(4B)
    Codec->>FEC: encode_bytes(data, pad_bits=2)
    FEC-->>Codec: FEC-encoded bytes (rate 1/2, k=7)
    Codec-->>TX: encoded bytes
    
    TX->>TX: build preamble(192b) + sync(32b) + fec bits
    TX->>Mod: bpsk_modulate(bitstream, SPS, alpha)
    Mod->>Mod: map bits → BPSK symbols, upsample, RRC filter
    Mod->>Mod: apply_burst_shaping (Hann ramps)
    Mod-->>TX: complex waveform
    
    TX->>Radio: SoapySDR stream (fc32 samples)
    Radio->>Air: RF @ 915 MHz
    Note over Air: 18 km path

    Air->>RX: RF @ fc + drift + fading + noise
    RX->>RX: digital AGC (normalize RMS)
    RX->>RX: scan_frequency (FO estimation)
    RX->>RX: mix to baseband
    RX->>RX: RRC matched filter
    RX->>RX: decimate × SPS (try all phases)
    RX->>RX: sync-word correlation (0xACDDA4E2)
    RX->>RX: extract FEC symbols
    RX->>Codec: packet_decode(fec_bytes)
    Codec->>FEC: decode_bytes_hard (Viterbi)
    FEC-->>Codec: decoded bits
    Codec->>Codec: read length, validate CRC
    Codec-->>RX: payload bytes (or None)
    RX-->>TX: decoded message printed

